        "reaction_type_english": "Oligomerization reaction",
        "description": "在固定床催化反应器中，于350°C和15 bar压力下，使用HZSM-5、Hβ和HY等多种沸石催化剂，将1-丁烯、顺-2-丁烯和反-2-丁烯组成的混合丁烯进行低聚反应，以生产喷气燃料范围（C8-C16）的碳氢化合物。研究了不同空速（WHSV 7-20 h⁻¹）和不同催化剂对转化率、选择性和产物分布的影响。",
        "text_snippet": "The oligomerization of mixed butene was carried out in a fixed-bed continuous-flow reactor (13 mm in diameter)... The reaction temperature and pressure of the reaction were 350 °C and 15 bar, respectively... The space velocity of the butene mixture [weight-hourly space velocity (WHSV), g-butene/g-dried catalyst/h] was varied between 7 and 20 h-1... Three types of zeolites, HZSM-5, Hβ and HY, were compared...",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Oligomer-Isomer reaction"
      }
    ]
